an','bidang-pertanian','2022-11-11 22:22:56','2022-11-11 22:22:56'),(30,'78738d1a-6252-11ed-b1d8-c3b1298f761c','Bidang Kehutanan','bidang-kehutanan','2022-11-11 22:23:06','2022-11-11 22:23:06'),(31,'7e626ef8-6252-11ed-b07c-0fc461b3ba58','Bidang Energi dan Sumber Daya Mineral','bidang-energi-dan-sumber-daya-mineral','2022-11-11 22:23:16','2022-11-11 22:23:16'),(32,'84281b6c-6252-11ed-a8e3-23171cace74c','Bidang Perdagangan','bidang-perdagangan','2022-11-11 22:23:26','2022-11-11 22:23:26'),(33,'8c3aeafa-6252-11ed-92ff-5d0fc048494e','Bidang Perindustrian','bidang-perindustrian','2022-11-11 22:23:39','2022-11-11 22:23:39'),(34,'92260e40-6252-11ed-afa6-0d5172533b03','Bidang Transmigrasi','bidang-transmigrasi','2022-11-11 22:23:49','2022-11-14 23:38:41');
